c: 9
v: 105
t: "Nabiyow ama jihaadak raaqe marak Yalli kicnim abaay Yalli niqbiimik exxeera Yallaa kee kay farmoytaay moominiin sin taama ablelek, isin Qhiyaamah ayro qellittam kee tambulleem yaaxigî (Yalla kinnuk) fanah gacsimetton, tokkel Yalli isin abba haak sugteenim siinih warsele keenik ixxic"